Package org.apache.calcite.test.schemata.catchall

Class CatchallSchema

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.test.schemata.catchall.CatchallSchema
  • public class CatchallSchema
extends Object
    Object whose fields are relations. Called "catch-all" because it's OK if tests add new fields.
